window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The fourth year at the Imperial Mage Academy brings a new set of challenges for Danny Youngblood. The discovery of a secret organization, the Deepcorp, lurking within the Imperial Palace, casts a long shadow over the Academy. As tensions rise between the Mages and the Corp, a mysterious creature known as the Shadow Crawler emerges, leaving a trail of frozen corpses in its wake. </p> <p>Accusations fly, friendships are tested, and Danny finds himself at the center of a conspiracy that threatens to tear the Empire apart.</p>"; 
